{"tid":1451544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情報系統 哨兵系統需要全面升級：屋企私家cam","createTime":"2019-08-11T19:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T10:59:34.000Z","uid":35776,"like":266,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"1d33c360e08acc7c0054c8c4d14d514bc72eb4fa","tid":1451544,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:21:43.000Z","msg":"屋企對住狗屋，向關鍵路口嘅<br />\n唔該自動自覺set 向街set cam<br />\n<br />\nset cam 重點：避免搵到身處樓層，<br />\n&gt;唔好影到水平樓層&gt;唔好伸出窗外&gt;要有遮蔽&gt;固定cam唔好拍片以免被逐層試試到，要用連還拍，電話不在此限，唔好影到同一棟樓及單位內擺設，包括冷氣機台，外牆顏色等，增加估計難度<br />\n<br />\n目標:每一個路口，每一批狗車經過都可以睇得見，增強情報覆蓋"},{"pid":"3ff24b563fda5f4258638211f6c239d8e3e3a6aa","tid":1451544,"uid":282624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:23:53.000Z","msg":"好有用"},{"pid":"6ea32dbe22faf192386b994209d8e924b6b30165","tid":1451544,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"febafdc3164374e6ec7368348088686db2ea88b4","tid":1451544,"uid":35776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:41:09.000Z","msg":"hkmap 系統大scale 上有用，但更新頻率同準確性有人check始終要提高"},{"pid":"101da57a48a9b6d66750837d696c130af9f9097e","tid":1451544,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:42:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bac52e690ac3bd444f465cc2f659a78515b702aa","tid":1451544,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d114df10b2fc40507047f169721e6c700827f58b","tid":1451544,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1e0b533dc4921dfb71d3ab865a1824e77c4431","tid":1451544,"uid":145496,"like":5,"dislike":