":1451544,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"另外影左相最好for ward 畀哨兵，有D web cam 唔係屋企都睇到嘅更好(當然注意資訊安全，唔好影到自己屋企"},{"pid":"1450b7a9a7df98cdfbaab6d2b0b48b0f9d18c6b4","tid":1451544,"uid":35776,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"3377b99dcfd07c5d72376118bbaa44e6f044a7e5","tid":1451544,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:29:01.000Z","msg":"對路口狗屋就係要zoom 近D <br />\n我已經教埋點樣避免自爆<br />\n<br />\n重申：set cam 唔係為左公開畀人實時mon，而係畀你自己mon完報哨兵台<br />\n<br />\n呢個係哨兵嘅擴大化計劃，經常夢遊唔得閒mon 私家cam嘅請你揀合適同更重要嘅一邊"},{"pid":"2191847e3180876730fb0fcaeae73530d0f09cd4","tid":1451544,"uid":35776,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:33:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">重申：私家cam唔係中門大開任人睇，我係要你地自己睇完私家cam情報報哨兵grp<br />\n<br />\n個cam 拍片其實冇問題，有機會拍到有價值嘅材料，但絕對唔好公開個cam畀人睇，並要做好資訊安全操施<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0eeebf4eda9ae28c4c7496e4f4f13acc61de7ac1","tid":1451544,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"b26637d058b9cfc603ae28ca2d3328ae06edd4a5","tid":1451544,"uid":166119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:39:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a09f769c53df70529163d4cdc95bb977eb82bd00","tid":1451544,"uid":71334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:40:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048902ad813b1ae02ad240c66baf466e915b2b0e","tid":1451544,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc203f33ed6154a8b320d9aa31a3d240affebf69","tid":1451544,"uid":35776,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"ac1e0b533dc4921dfb71d3ab865a1824e77c4431","tid":1451544,"uid":145496,"li